###
### Get All Items (for reference)
GET http://localhost:8081/pahana-edu-api/api/items
Accept: application/json

###
### Create a New Item
POST http://localhost:8081/pahana-edu-api/api/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "NEW-BOOK-001",
  "name": "The Hitchhiker's Guide",
  "description": "A classic sci-fi comedy.",
  "category": "Science Fiction",
  "author": "Douglas Adams",
  "price": 14.99,
  "stockQuantity": 42
}

###
### Create an Item with Invalid Data (to test validation)
POST http://localhost:8081/pahana-edu-api/api/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "BAD-SKU-001",
  "name": "Book with Negative Price",
  "price": -5.00,
  "stockQuantity": 10
}

###
### Update an Existing Item (Change ID in URL to match one in your DB)
PUT http://localhost:8081/pahana-edu-api/api/items/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "BOOK-HC-001-UPDATED",
  "name": "The Midnight Library (Updated Edition)",
  "description": "A classic story about choices.",
  "category": "Modern Fiction",
  "author": "Matt Haig",
  "price": 16.99,
  "stockQuantity": 45
}

###
### Delete an Existing Item (Change ID to one you want to delete)
DELETE http://localhost:8081/pahana-edu-api/api/items/4